  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304750/extras/a39ebbab527779928da33534c5b1e415.poster.avif?t=1741658415\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304750/extras/a39ebbab527779928da33534c5b1e415.webm?t=1741658415\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304750/extras/a39ebbab527779928da33534c5b1e415.mp4?t=1741658415\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the shoes of Agent Kim, a seasoned private investigator drawn into a chilling mystery deep in the wilderness. Nine people have vanished from an eerie villa over the past 20 years, including your latest client’s adventurous relative, Mr. Lin. The police have failed to uncover any leads, leaving the task of solving this haunting puzzle to you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304750/extras/cd4de596ae33d342dd0c422d97e45a51.poster.avif?t=1741658415\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304750/extras/cd4de596ae33d342dd0c422d97e45a51.webm?t=1741658415\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304750/extras/cd4de596ae33d342dd0c422d97e45a51.mp4?t=1741658415\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After sneaking into the villa, you’re struck by an unknown force and awaken in a cold, desolate room. The air is thick with dread as you realize you’ve become the latest prisoner of this cursed mansion. With danger lurking around every corner and the undead stalking your every move, it’s a race against time to escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304750/extras/d112ebb5746e56f9792e2334a757f986.poster.avif?t=1741658415\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304750/extras/d112ebb5746e56f9792e2334a757f986.webm?t=1741658415\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304750/extras/d112ebb5746e56f9792e2334a757f986.mp4?t=1741658415\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the villa’s dark corridors, uncover its sinister past, and piece together the terrifying truth behind the disappearances. Find hidden clues, solve intricate puzzles, and outsmart the relentless zombies that roam the estate. Your only hope is to escape before becoming another soul lost to the mansion’s curse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304750/extras/c9f711270a0af4ca5ad3c4fa32a57cba.poster.avif?t=1741658415\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304750/extras/c9f711270a0af4ca5ad3c4fa32a57cba.webm?t=1741658415\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304750/extras/c9f711270a0af4ca5ad3c4fa32a57cba.mp4?t=1741658415\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you make it out alive, or will you too vanish without a trace?</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304750/extras/a39ebbab527779928da33534c5b1e415.poster.avif?t=1741658415\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304750/extras/a39ebbab527779928da33534c5b1e415.webm?t=1741658415\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304750/extras/a39ebbab527779928da33534c5b1e415.mp4?t=1741658415\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the shoes of Agent Kim, a seasoned private investigator drawn into a chilling mystery deep in the wilderness. Nine people have vanished from an eerie villa over the past 20 years, including your latest client’s adventurous relative, Mr. Lin. The police have failed to uncover any leads, leaving the task of solving this haunting puzzle to you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304750/extras/cd4de596ae33d342dd0c422d97e45a51.poster.avif?t=1741658415\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304750/extras/cd4de596ae33d342dd0c422d97e45a51.webm?t=1741658415\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304750/extras/cd4de596ae33d342dd0c422d97e45a51.mp4?t=1741658415\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After sneaking into the villa, you’re struck by an unknown force and awaken in a cold, desolate room. The air is thick with dread as you realize you’ve become the latest prisoner of this cursed mansion. With danger lurking around every corner and the undead stalking your every move, it’s a race against time to escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304750/extras/d112ebb5746e56f9792e2334a757f986.poster.avif?t=1741658415\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304750/extras/d112ebb5746e56f9792e2334a757f986.webm?t=1741658415\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304750/extras/d112ebb5746e56f9792e2334a757f986.mp4?t=1741658415\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the villa’s dark corridors, uncover its sinister past, and piece together the terrifying truth behind the disappearances. Find hidden clues, solve intricate puzzles, and outsmart the relentless zombies that roam the estate. Your only hope is to escape before becoming another soul lost to the mansion’s curse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304750/extras/c9f711270a0af4ca5ad3c4fa32a57cba.poster.avif?t=1741658415\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304750/extras/c9f711270a0af4ca5ad3c4fa32a57cba.webm?t=1741658415\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304750/extras/c9f711270a0af4ca5ad3c4fa32a57cba.mp4?t=1741658415\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you make it out alive, or will you too vanish without a trace?</p>",
